text: Las Lomas is a corregimiento in La Pintada District, Coclé Province, Panama. It has a land area of and had a population of 2,072 as of 2010, giving it a population density of . It was created by Law 56 of December 5, 2002. ==References== Category:Corregimientos of Coclé Province
